11#include "logging/rtc_event_log/events/rtc_event_alr_state.h"
12
13#include "absl/memory/memory.h"
14
15namespace webrtc {
16
17RtcEventAlrState::RtcEventAlrState(bool in_alr) : in_alr_(in_alr) {}
18
19RtcEventAlrState::RtcEventAlrState(const RtcEventAlrState& other)
20 : RtcEvent(other.timestamp_us_), in_alr_(other.in_alr_) {}
21
22RtcEventAlrState::~RtcEventAlrState() = default;
23
24std::unique_ptr<RtcEventAlrState> RtcEventAlrState::Copy() const {
25 return absl::WrapUnique<RtcEventAlrState>(new RtcEventAlrState(*this));
26}

28} // namespace webrtc
